    FIX: Manual image upload crashes and broken image handling
    
    Issues fixed:
    1. Manual image upload preview not showing
    2. 'Cannot read properties of undefined (reading src)' error
    3. Broken images causing storefront crashes
    
    Solutions implemented:
    - Added proper file validation (type, size)
    - Enhanced error handling with detailed messages
    - Added image URL validation before rendering
    - Added onError handler to remove broken images
    - Filter invalid URLs before sending to server
    - Better user feedback for upload status
    
    This should fix the manual product creation flow completely.

